  "remarks": "Sanam Industrial Group was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: Entities involved in nuclear or ballistic missile activities. (subordinate to AIO, which has purchased equipment on AIO’s behalf for the missile programme).\n\nThe Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
